item.title: [Delta]26 Compile Errors[317]
item.dc:creator: @reward reward
item.description:
@reward wrote:

[quote=“mrpopyman, post:4, topic:397853”][quote author=reward link=topic=494988.msg3619012#msg3619012 date=1307233201]

Show the very first error.

Class8.java:6194: illegal start of expression public static final Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1 method200(int i, int j, int, k, int l); ^

that’s exactly what it says
[/quote]

Should be easy to fix, i think you may have forgotten to put a “;” in some places

eg:

Wrong home command strip:

if(command.equalsIgnoreCase("home")) { if(!inCombat) { toX =3088 toY = 3493 heightLevel = 0 } else { sM("You must be out of combat to teleport") } }

Correct:

if(command.equalsIgnoreCase("home")) { if(!inCombat) { toX =3088; toY = 3493; heightLevel = 0; } else { sM("You must be out of combat to teleport"); } }

you have to add the ;'s in the spaces they need to be in[/quote]
checked and i saw nothing
